item.title: Renovations
item.description: Every home needs updating after a while. Fortunately, Jabbar’s General Contracting has done hundreds of renovation projects. Everything from bathrooms and kitchens to entire homes, nothing is outside of the scope of what we can do!

item.title: Repairs
item.description: We can repair any job fast and make sure that your problems don’t become more costly. Jabbar’s General Contracting personally stands by any repair made and guarantees that it will be fixed right!
